{"abstract":[{"text":"Suggestion chip is a UI element that allows to present recommended or predictive options based on user’s input or context,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and is commonly used to capture filtering decisions.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Suggestion chip is typically non-selected by default and can be tapped or clicked to apply the suggestion, streamlining input and enhancing usability.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Chips can show multiple interactive elements together in the same area, such as a list of selectable movie times, or a serie of email contacts.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Best suited for category-based filters that do not require additional visual elements.","type":"text"}],"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip\/init(_:tableName:bundle:action:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip\/init(icon:_:tableName:bundle:action:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip\/init(icon:accessibilityLabel:action:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip\/init(icon:accessibilityLabel:tableName:bundle:action:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip\/init(icon:text:action:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip\/init(text:action:)"],"title":"Initializers","generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip\/body"],"title":"Instance Properties","generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip\/View-Implementations"],"title":"Default Implementations","g